Output assets/demo.gif

Require echo

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 32
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600

Type "./mora_jai_box.py" Sleep 500ms  Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "byg" Sleep 500ms  Enter
Type "yGy" Sleep 500ms  Enter
Type "gyb" Sleep 500ms  Enter

Sleep 1s

Type "yy" Sleep 500ms  Enter
Type "yy" Sleep 500ms  Enter

Sleep 1s

ScrollUp@10ms 50
ScrollDown@0.2s 50

Sleep 5s
